### ============================================
### PASO 1: CREAR LOTES EXPIRADOS EN ITEMSTOCK 18
### ============================================

### Lote Expirado 1: 50kg, ItemStock 18, vence 01/Enero 2026 (PASADO - 67 días)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/stock-batch
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "itemStockId": 18,
  "quantity": 50,
  "supplierId": 4,
  "batchNumber": "LOTE-EXP-001",
  "expiryDate": "2026-01-01"
}

